dct_title_s: Engellandt mit dem anstossenden Reich Schottlandt, so vorzeiten Albion und Britannia haben geheissen [verso]
dct_description_sm: Covers Great Britain and eastern Ireland. Relief shown pictorially. Appears in Münster's Cosmographia. 1588. Oriented with north to the right. Includes text and ill. Signature mark on verso: iiii. Other title on verso.
